The product owner is a servant leader accountable for making decisions when the [[Product Squad]] cannot reach a unanimous consensus about  [[Acceptance Criteria]] and priorities. The product owner is also responsible for answering [[Delivery Squad]] questions about the product when the [[Product Squad]] isn't conveniently available. 